## Checklist to finish

1. Unzip events_app_champagne_revA.zip into `events_app/` (replace when asked).
2. Delete old files that import shared_preferences.
3. Follow SETUP.md steps 3–5 (this creates file B2).
4. Add P3–P5 at the repo root.
5. Commit and push: `git add -A && git commit -m "Champagne rev A — BRIEF-001 build" && git push`
